service: banking-bot

provider:
  name: aws
  runtime: nodejs18.x
  region: us-east-1
  environment:
    NODE_ENV: ${env:NODE_ENV, 'development'}

plugins:
  - serverless-offline

functions:
  handler:
    handler: apps/handler/src/main.lambda
    events:
      - http:
          path: handler
          method: post

  consumer:
    handler: apps/consumer/src/main.lambda
    events:
      - http:
          path: consumer
          method: post

custom:
  serverless-offline:
    httpPort: 3000
    lambdaPort: 3002
